pull_request.title: change sphincs variant enablement
pull_request.body:
Changes the default enablement settings for some Sphincs+ algorithms to activate variants [favoured by NIST](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/blob/cf6d8a059e446d24e2af06949d83605ae0f4f414/.CMake/alg_support.cmake#L542).

- [x] documentation is added or updated
- [na] tests are added or updated

Enables profiling of NIST-standardized sig algs as per https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/pull/86

repo.name: openssl
repo.description: Fork of OpenSSL that includes prototype quantum-resistant algorithms and ciphersuites based on liboqs
